{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/blade-ui-kit/awesome-tall-stack/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fdf56d9c-06a3-5872-9dea-df2ccfab28a4","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-tall-stack-awesome-lint-awesome-list\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-tall-stack-awesome-lint-awesome-list\" aria-label=\"awesome tall stack awesome lint awesome list permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome TALL Stack <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a> <img src=\"https://github.com/blade-ui-kit/awesome-tall-stack/workflows/Lint%20Awesome%20List/badge.svg\" alt=\"Lint Awesome List\"></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A curated list of awesome things related to the TALL stack.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://tallstack.dev/\">TALL stack</a> is a full stack development solution featuring some of the libraries built by the Laravel community. It features tools that allows you to write apps with a focus on backend and without having to write too much JavaScript, thus allowing you to focus on a smaller set of programming tools.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#the-tall-stack\">The TALL Stack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#community-websites\">Community Websites</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#libraries\">Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#learning\">Learning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#examples\">Examples</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"the-tall-stack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-tall-stack\" aria-label=\"the tall stack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The TALL Stack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com\">Tailwind CSS</a> - (<a href=\"https://github.com/aniftyco/awesome-tailwindcss\">Awesome List</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/aniftyco/awesome-tailwindcss\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6.6k</span></span></a>) - A utility-first CSS framework for rapidly building custom designs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/alpinejs/alpine\">Alpine.js</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/alpinejs/alpine\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">16k</span></span></a> - (<a href=\"https://github.com/alpinejs/awesome-alpine\">Awesome List</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/alpinejs/awesome-alpine\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">539</span></span></a>) - A rugged, minimal framework for composing JavaScript behavior in your markup.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://laravel-livewire.com\">Livewire</a> - (<a href=\"https://github.com/imliam/awesome-livewire\">Awesome List</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/imliam/awesome-livewire\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">296</span></span></a>) - A full-stack framework for Laravel that takes the pain out of building dynamic UIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com\">Laravel</a> - (<a href=\"https://github.com/chiraggude/awesome-laravel\">Awesome List</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/chiraggude/awesome-laravel\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">10.2k</span></span></a>) - A PHP web application framework with expressive, elegant syntax.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community-websites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community-websites\" aria-label=\"community websites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community Websites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://talltips.novate.co.uk/\">talltips</a> - Collection of tips and ideas across the TALL stack.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"libraries\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#libraries\" aria-label=\"libraries permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Libraries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.alptail.com\">Alptail</a> - A collection of open-source UI components, using Tailwind CSS and Alpine.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/blade-ui-kit/blade-icons\">Blade Icons</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/blade-ui-kit/blade-icons\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.3k</span></span></a> - A package to easily make use of SVG icons in your Laravel Blade views.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cbl/blade-script\">Blade Script</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/cbl/blade-script\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">36</span></span></a> - A package to easily add transpiled &#x26; minified scripts to your Blade components.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cbl/blade-style\">Blade Style</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/cbl/blade-style\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">11</span></span></a> - A package to easily minify styles and make use of sass, less, etc. in your Blade components.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blade-ui-kit.com/\">Blade UI Kit</a> - A set of renderless components to utilise in your Laravel Blade views.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/aw-studio/docdress\">Docdress</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/aw-studio/docdress\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">41</span></span></a> - A package to create markdown documentations from GitHub repositories in a Laravel-like design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://filamentadmin.com\">Filament</a> - The elegant TALL stack admin panel for Laravel artisans.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pascalbaljetmedia/laravel-form-components\">Laravel Form Components</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/pascalbaljetmedia/laravel-form-components\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">324</span></span></a> - A set of Blade components to rapidly build forms with Tailwind CSS Custom Forms and Bootstrap 4.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/laravel-frontend-presets/tall\">Laravel TALL Preset</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/laravel-frontend-presets/tall\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.2k</span></span></a> - A front-end preset for Laravel to scaffold an application using the TALL stack.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/use-preset/laravel-tall/\">Laravel TALL Preset</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/use-preset/laravel-tall/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7</spa